HEADWORD: Juncaceae
<hw>Juncaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A natural family of tufted herbs
resembling grasses, including the true <members>rushes</members>; called
also the <altname>rush family</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Juncaceae</fam>, rush family.</syn>⟦br⟧
